## Naming conventions

| Artifact | Convention |
|----------|-----------|
| API struct type | `API_<Domain>` |
| API def resolver constant | `ApiDef_<Domain>` |
| Backend handler method | `<actionName>` (matches API struct key) |
| Frontend caller method | `<actionName>` (matches API struct key) |
| File name | `api-def.ts` |
